<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l9"><expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> beſchedigung <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> als dir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>perlaching<ex>ern</ex></expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l10">ſeÿ / . waiſt du <expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan> wol / daʒ <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> armen <expan>lewt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>deſgleich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l12">von Jn auch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_335_line_1576487627634_4950">vnpilleich </ab><ab facs="#facs_335_line_1576487629560_4955">vnd vngüt </ab><ab facs="#facs_335_line_1576487631480_4960"><expan>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ıſt / vnd wiſſen dir darauf nicht 
