<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l15"><expan>cʒeantwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / dann das vns das <expan>getrewlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> leid ıſt / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_335_r1l17"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııj̃ . <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Lamp<ex>er</ex>tȷ</expan> / . </ab>
